Day 47: Docker Python App

Date: October 14, 2025
Overview
Containerized a Python application with dependencies.
Key Concepts Learned

Python Docker best practices
Requirements.txt handling
Virtual environments in containers
Application configuration

Commands Used
dockerfileFROM python:3.9
WORKDIR /app
COPY requirements.txt .
RUN pip install -r requirements.txt
COPY . .
CMD ["python", "app.py"]
Challenges Faced
Python dependency conflicts and ensuring the container had all required packages. Managing image size was also a concern.
